library(tidyquant)
library(tidyverse)
library(tsibble)
library(fable)
library(feasts)
data = tq_get(c("DIS", "AMZN"), get = "stock.prices", from = "2023-01-01", to = "2024-03-29") %>% select(symbol, date, adjusted)
data
data = data %>% group_by(symbol) %>% mutate(t = row_number())
data = as_tsibble(data, key = symbol, index = t)
data
?NNETAR
report(filter(fit, symbol == "AMZN"))
Error in UseMethod("report") : 
  no applicable method for 'report' applied to an object of class "c('mdl_df', 'tbl_df', 'tbl', 'data.frame')"
accuracy(fit)
fit %>%
  forecast(h = 20) %>%
  autoplot(data)
